### **2. 32_APIFlowRadar**  
**Description:**  
Tracks the flow of multiple API endpoints and visualizes response time variations and availability dips.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# APIFlowRadar - Real-Time Endpoint Latency Monitor

APIFlowRadar provides insights into performance drift, bottlenecks, and sudden failures across multiple endpoints.

## Features
- Real-time response tracking  
- CSV / JSON export  
- Status + latency logging  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/32_APIFlowRadar.git
cd 32_APIFlowRadar
python monitor.py
